data.text: List of Academy Award for Best Cinematography winners from every year the award has been given out. All Academy Award for Best Cinematography winners are listed below in order of popularity, but can be sorted by any column. People who won the Academy Award for Best Cinematography award are listed along with photos for every Academy Award for Best Cinematography winner that has a picture associated with their name online. You can click on the name of the Academy Award for Best Cinematography award recipients to get more information about each. People who won the Academy Award for Best Cinematography are usually listed by year, but on this list you've got a complete list of Academy Award for Best Cinematography winners from all years. If this proves to not be a full list of Academy Award for Best Cinematography winners, you can help make it so by adding to this one. This list includes the most memorable and well-known Academy Award for Best Cinematography winners of all time. Anybody who won the Academy Award for Best Cinematography usually has a picture associated with their name, so all the Academy Award for Best Cinematography-winning people are listed here with photos when available. This list spans the history of the Academy Award for Best Cinematography, so most of the famous Academy Award for Best Cinematography winners are here and can be a good starting point for making a list of your favorites. This list answers the question "who are all the people who have ever won Academy Award for Best Cinematography?" If you're looking for all the nominees, you can click the links above the title of this page to the Listopedia page where you'll find a directory of award nominees, as well as the rest of the award winners lists we have. You may want to copy this fact-based list to build your own just like it, re-rank it to fit your opinions, then publish it to share it on Facebook, Twitter or any other social sites you frequent. List features items like Robert Surtees, John Toll and more! {#nodes}
